text: Seui (Seùi) is a town and comune (municipality) in the Province of Sud Sardegna in Sardinia, Italy. As of 2016, 1,291 people lived there. Its area is 148.21 km².Istituto nazionale di statistica - Superficie territoriale per zona altimetrica It is 820 meters above sea level. == References == == Other websites == Category:Communes of the Province of South Sardinia
